      <entry xml:id="entry_læqqūg" xml:lang="os" abv:completeness="questions">
        <form type="lemma" xml:lang="os-x-iron"><orth>læqqūg</orth></form>
        <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>qwælæg</orth></form>
        <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
            <q>тухлый</q>
            <note xml:lang="ru" type="comment"> (о яйце)</note>
            
          </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
            <q>rotten</q>
            <note type="comment"> (of egg)</note>
          </abv:tr></sense>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma" xml:lang="os-x-iron"><orth>læqqūg ajk</orth></form>
          <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>qwælæg ajkæ</orth></form>
          <sense><sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
                <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">тухлое яйцо</q>
              </tr><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="en">
                <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">rotten egg</q>
              </tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                <q>болтун</q>
              </abv:tr><?oxy_comment_start author="oleg" timestamp="20220329T234318+0300" comment="do something about this"?></sense><?oxy_comment_end?></sense>
        </re>
        <etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
              <phr>laqu (kaka)</phr></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/>
              <phr>laqvi (kʼvercxi)</phr></mentioned>
            <gloss><q>тухлое (яйцо)</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/>
            <w>laq</w>
            <gloss><q>попорченное яйцо</q></gloss>
            <note type="bibl">(<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Радлов"/>
                <biblScope>III 728</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>. Первоисточник —
            <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
            <w>laq</w>
            <gloss><q>тухлое яйцо</q></gloss>
            <note type="bibl">(<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Гаффаров"/>
                <biblScope>II 716</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>. Семантика ведет,
          по-видимому, к <q rendition="#rend_doublequotes">болтать</q>, как в <mentioned
            xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
            <w>болтун</w>
            <gloss><q>негодное, неплодное яйцо</q></gloss></mentioned>; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="tg"><lang/>
            <w>laqqīdan</w>
            <gloss><q>болтать</q></gloss>
            <note type="bibl">(<bibl><title>Тадж.-русск. сл.</title>
                <pubPlace>М.</pubPlace>, <date>1954</date>, <biblScope>стр.
              205</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>. — Дигорская форма <oRef
            xml:lang="os-x-digor">qwælæg</oRef> должна рассматриваться как видоизменение иронской
          (метатеза согласных и перебой гласного).</etym>
        <etym xml:lang="en">Cf. <mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
              <phr>laqu (kaka)</phr></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/>
              <phr>laqvi (kʼvercxi)</phr></mentioned>
            <gloss><q>rotten (egg)</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/>
            <w>laq</w>
            <gloss><q>spoiled egg</q></gloss>
            <note type="bibl">(<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Радлов"/>
                <biblScope>III 728</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>. The original source is
            <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
            <w>laq</w>
            <gloss><q>rotten egg</q></gloss>
            <note type="bibl">(<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Гаффаров"/>
                <biblScope>II 716</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>. The semantics probably
          leads to <q rendition="#rend_doublequotes">shake</q>, as in <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
            <w>boltun</w>
            <gloss><q>useless, fruitless egg</q></gloss>, <gloss>lit.
            <q>shaker</q></gloss></mentioned>; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="tg"><lang/>
            <w>laqqīdan</w>
            <gloss><q>shake</q></gloss>
            <note type="bibl">(<bibl><title>Tajik-Russian dictionary</title>.
                  <pubPlace>Мoscow</pubPlace>, <date>1954</date>, <biblScope>p.
                205</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>. — The Digor form <oRef
            xml:lang="os-x-digor">qwælæg</oRef> must be viewed as modified from Iron (consonant
          metathesis and vowel alternation).</etym>
      </entry>
